                                    <div class="elementor-widget-container">
                                        <p>Today, Muliya – Gold &amp; Diamonds is a symbol of elegance, trust, and forward-thinking craftsmanship. With over 81 years of heritage, we proudly serve customers through 7 showrooms across Karnataka, including
